mixin carousel
    #myCarousel.carousel.slide
        ol.carousel-indicators
            li.active(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='0')
            li(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='1')
            li(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='2')
        .carousel-inner
            .item.active
                img(src='http://www.rhetorik-seminar-online.com/public/files/Staedte/Stuttgart.jpg', alt='First slide')
                .container
                    .carousel-caption
                        h1 Example headline.
                        p
                            | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit.
                        p
                            a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='#') Sign up today
            .item
                img(src='http://congress.stuttgart-tourist.de/img/a/b/d/q/u/x/y/c/stuttgart-by-car.jpeg,', alt='Second slide')
                .container
                    .carousel-caption
                        h1 Another example headline.
                        p
                            | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit.
                        p
                            a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='#') Learn more
            .item
                img(src='https://www.freude-am-fliegen.de/tl_files/Rall_Rundfluege/Stuttgart-Ludwigsburg-Flug/Fernsehturm%20Stuttgart.jpg', alt='Third slide')
                .container
                    .carousel-caption
                        h1 One more for good measure.
                        p
                            | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit.
                        p
                            a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='#') Browse gallery
        a.left.carousel-control(href='#myCarousel', data-slide='prev')
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-left
        a.right.carousel-control(href='#myCarousel', data-slide='next')
            span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-right